OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and dry day with
OL,6,Fpossibly some patchy cloud around at
OL,7,Ftimes, mostly in the northwest.
OL,8,FFeeling very warm in the sunshine, but
OL,9,Fturning hazy later. Light winds
OL,10,Fthroughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying mostly clear and dry
OL,13,Fwith some lower cloud moving into the
OL,14,Fwest later. Mist and fog developing in
OL,15,Fprone spots. Staying mild overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA warm start to the day, but
OL,18,Fcloud and rain moves into the west
OL,19,Fthrough the morning. Clears eastwards
OL,20,Finto the afternoon, leaving cooler and
OL,21,Fshowery weather across the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
