OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Funsettled on Friday and Saturday with
OL,7,Ffurther rain at times, mainly on
OL,8,FSaturday. Turning more showery again
OL,9,Fon Sunday. Temperatures nearer to
OL,10,Faverage.
